This is a collection of TextMate Bundles added as git submodules from other repositories.


Examples for working with git submodules:


Add an external repository
=========================
git submodule add git://github.com/dchelimsky/rspec.git rspec

Get data into submodule directory
=================================
Before we can actually use our repository, we have to initialise
and update all the submodules. That's achieved with from the main repository root:

git submodule init
git submodule update


All listed examples and commands are taken from Graeme Mathieson (aka mathie) http://woss.name/blog/2008/4/9/using-git-submodules-to-track-plugins.html.